{"comments":"Spotlight Morphing — Shape interpolation between tour targets.\n\n## Overview\n\nWhen transitioning between tour steps, the spotlight doesn't just\nappear/disappear — it MORPHS from one shape/position to another.\nThis creates spatial continuity and helps users track where they are.\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\nMorphing uses spring physics for organic movement, with optional:\n- Scale pop at midpoint (draws attention)\n- Rotation at midpoint (adds life)\n- Curved paths for distant targets (avoids diagonal motion)\n\nThe result feels like a living entity guiding the user.\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Configuration for spotlight morph transitions between targets.\n\nWhen transitioning from step N to step N+1, the highlight morphs\nfrom one shape/position to another with configurable physics.\n","info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"typeSynonym","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["duration",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["spring",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Compound","Tour","Motion","Spring"],"SpringParams"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["interpolation",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Compound","Tour","Motion","Spotlight"],"MorphInterpolation"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["pathCurve",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["scaleAtMidpoint",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["rotateAtMidpoint",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["opacityDip",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons